          <text>
                    <body>
                              <div xml:id="d.1">
                                        <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to István Brodarics (?)
                                                  (Brussels, 15 July 1531)</head>
                                        <floatingText type="regesta">
                                                  <body>
                                                  <p xml:id="reg.p.1"> He is happy that S. is well.
                                                  He wished he could have been beside him during his
                                                  troubles, that would have eased his pain.</p>
                                                  </body>
                                        </floatingText>
                                        <pb facs="https://www.eleveltar.hu/kereso-portlet/spring/digitalcontent/getcontent/preservica/95946FF5-EF98-48F1-963F-4801AEAD1960
                                                  "/>
                                        <p xml:id="p.1"> Ad eundem.<note xml:id="note.1">See Ep.
                                                  159. Note
                                                  1.<ref>olahus.tei.15310711_1</ref></note></p>
                                        <p xml:id="p.2">Bene te valere gaudeo, valeo utcumque ego
                                                  quoque, utinam melius valerem. Res tuas prosperas
                                                  libenter audivi; non deerunt inimici rebus
                                                  prosperis, qui te expugnent, fortiter his pro tuo
                                                  more resistas. Vellem, ut scribis, in meis rebus
                                                  adversis adfuisses, doloris minus habuissem, nec
                                                  ego nec tu tantis fuissemus malis affecti. Quantum
                                                  enim mutua societas et conversatio detrahat malis,
                                                  eaque leniat, iampridem satis es expertus. Ego
                                                  quoque non sum nescius. Vale.</p>
                                        <p xml:id="p.3"><placeName>Bruxellae</placeName> XV. Iulii
                                                  1531.</p>
                              </div>
